      • tryRemove

        public boolean tryRemove(ChunkLocation location)
        Attempts to remove the chunk from memory and save it

        This method returns false if:

        • The chunk is not loaded
        • The chunk still has strong references

        Parameters:
        location - the location to remove the chunk
        Returns:
        true to signify that the collection was modified as a result of this operation
